      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MIA PARTY GIRL (1) recorded a 3 length third in a Maiden last time 23.31 at this track and trip and also jumping from the same draw. Has the ability and looks hard to top. PROJECT NEMESIS (2) put in a much better performance last start when in the placings at this track behind Reborn Harmony (23.38) in a Maiden. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Expected to be in this for a long way. US TWO BOYS (8) turned in a plain effort last time when eighth at Taree Super Track over 300m behind Try To Relax (18.31) in a Maiden. Comes out of a solid form race last start. Will give the top chances plenty to think about. PRINCESS ENERGY (6) cannot be overlooked following a recent top-three finish.",
